<section id="contact" class="orders text-center">
  <div class="container order-content">
    <h2>Online Ordering Coming Soon</h2>
    <p>We're currently perfecting our online ordering system. In the meantime, you can find us at the Running Creek local market every Saturday morning.</p>
    <div class="contact-info mt-4">
      <p>Have a question or want to pre-order? Contact us:</p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@runningcreeksourdough.com.au" class="email-link">hello@runningcreeksourdough.com.au</a>
